Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Why Vance quit
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w1zp
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 4 May 1980
Point of principle lay behind resignation of Secretary of State Cyrus Vance following secrecy over hostage rescue attempt. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less